# Project layout reference

Use when creating or navigating cluster/Talos/Flux files.

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `talconfig.yaml` | Talos cluster layout |
| `clusterenv.yaml` | Chart + Talos variables (plaintext; encrypt with clustertool) |
| `talsecret.yaml` | Talos encryption keys |
| `age.agekey` | SOPS age key — **local only, never commit**; keep an offline backup |
| `.sops.yaml` | SOPS encryption rules |
| `.pre-commit-config.yaml` | pre-commit hooks |
| `talconfig.json` | Schema for `talconfig.yaml` |
| `/patches/` | Stock Talos machine patches (don't alter stock; you may add your own) |
| `/generated/` | Bootstrap / Flux-consumed generated files |
| `.devcontainer` | Dev container for clustertool |
| `.vscode` | Recommended VS Code extensions |
| `/repositories/` | Flux HelmRepository defs |
| `/clusters/` | Cluster definitions (this repo may host multiple) |
| `/kubernetes/` | Per-cluster Kubernetes manifests (under `clusters/<name>/`) |
| `/custom_images/` | Custom Docker images built by CI |
| Homelab docs | [nerd.dad](https://github.com/nerddotdad/nerd.dad) → `docs/homelab/` (GitHub Pages) |

Example TrueCharts clusters for patterns:

- https://github.com/alfi0812/talos
- https://github.com/kqmaverick/cluster
